description:
TOCD Studio is open-sourced & onchain Studio developing solutions with gamification for people's needs. So far for the past 2 years, we developed 4 products:  
> The Old Castle Defense - Onchain game with $500,000+ earned by users and 30,000 active players;
> DRS - onchain referral system with instant rewards; 
> FGE (Frame Generated Engine) - An open-sourced framework for Farcaster frames. Create Frames without code needs;
> $FOMO - Community Meme Token;
